s.title: Scripts-MKS Einstellungen
s.information:
Welcome! Thanks for using this script. If you would like more information, you could always look at the site. Do you have any questions? Please contact me at the Dutch forum, Discordmessage: JRH1997#2625, Github JRH-1997 or ingame message at the dutch game www.meldkamerspel.com: JRH1997
If you would change some translations or add descriptions to settings, feel free to contribute on Github.
s.restoreMessage: Are you sure you want to restore all settings of the script?

hotkey.title: Hotkeys
hotkey.moduledescription: Um einen Hotkey zu ändern, können Sie auf das Eingabefeld dieses Hotkeys klicken und die gewünschte Taste drücken. Die neue Schaltfläche wird automatisch angezeigt und gespeichert.

general.telemetry.title: Data collection
general.telemetry.description: We collect usage data and error logging. These data include: user ID, username, gameversion, Script settings and script version. If it's an error report, then the data will also includes the Error message. We only use this information for support, statistics and finding/resolving bugs
